INSERT INTO `tb_item_desc` VALUES ('973267', '<div class=\"content_tpl\"><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t304/143/177292392/116265/72e8ec71/54042992Nbf9523b6.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t349/254/186340024/304241/f2d1d2e6/54042998N68927004.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-2\" name=\"detail-tag-id-2\" text=\"适用范围\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>适用范围</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Heritage</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t211/13/2003601313/399493/ca6464e2/540429a0N1a26ebca.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-4\" name=\"detail-tag-id-4\" text=\"产品特色\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>产品特色</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Selling Point</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t295/181/175462546/13800/4a36697d/540429a9N9a7119e2.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t229/54/2016809130/355991/75b3fa1c/54042aecNf86a4772.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">在对讲功能的基础上，采用高通公司完美解决方案结合电信网络和GPS的技术，让用户在使用中得到更多的服务和技术支持。具有即时定位、历史移动轨迹、电子栅栏功能，室内误差在50米，精确度高。通过电脑网页管控，不需要添加任何的设备。（注：开通此功能请咨询免费客服400-007-2919）</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t343/157/176807567/258134/2f953401/54042af9Na41edf66.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t211/66/2071884121/188611/23f29ba6/54042b01N6445a7a1.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-10\" name=\"detail-tag-id-10\" text=\"产品信息\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>产品信息</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Product Information</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t289/108/171774434/118801/162da082/54042b6fN14ef607e.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t304/119/172072520/114307/817f644/54042b77N6c4a5a80.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t283/5/174450554/195442/b4562111/54042bc2Nc778aae4.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">临时组呼：用户直接在终端上根据地址本信息，创建临时组，发起呼叫，群组信息保存在终端中。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">呼叫限制：可以限制用户的某类呼叫能力，包括呼入和呼出限制，如单呼、组呼、聊天室等。\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">预定义组呼：预定义群组由集团管理员创建并管理，群组信息保存在电信服务器中，群组名字自动同步到终端。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">业务优先级：指设定对讲机、普通电话和上网等各种业务之间的优先级。如普通电话的优先级高于对讲机，则用户在对讲过程中如有电话打进，对讲功能将被关闭。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">成员优先级：指同一群组内可设置不同的话权优先级。优先级高的用户可优先获得话权，当优先级低的用户在发言时，优先级高的用户可抢占其话语权。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t220/68/2028131900/161066/2db7cb66/54042c26N1bb99aef.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t223/141/2043807293/81538/fa35e88b/54042c38N554381e6.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-21\" name=\"detail-tag-id-21\" text=\"品牌介绍\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>品牌介绍</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Bra