bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/jfs/t382/300/424252420/9695/8779e608/541bd9f6N2958851e.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 14px\" class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><br /></span><br /><div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">&nbsp;注：选择购机入网送话费的方式购买合约，话费为赠品不开具发票</span></div></div><div style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; FONT-FAMILY: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; FONT-SIZE: 14px\" class=\"formwork_img\"><div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"></span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"formwork_bt\"><div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#ffffff;\"></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">艺术设计</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">匠心独具的设计</span><br />流畅简洁的机身线条，纹理触感设计的后盖，彰显经典与永恒韵味的侧面齿状花纹，外加精心的拼接处理，凝铸为匠心独具的GALAXY Note3。简约而不简单的制作工艺，带来卓尔不群的外形和手感。5.7英寸全高清炫丽大屏，让精彩内容一览无余；分辨率高达1920×1080，屏幕更大的同时显示更细腻更自然，让您的视界更宽广、视觉体验更丰富。GALAXY Note3，让功能和艺术设计平衡<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\">，华丽</span>绽放。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g15/M02/0B/05/rBEhWFI6yvoIAAAAAACeQ3KdpkcAADUJQA5rpcAAJ5b541.jpg\" /></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">S Pen浮窗指令</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">魔法生活的开始<br /></span>GALAXY Note3的S Pen浮窗指令宛如神奇的魔法，助您瞬间完成各项指令。您只需将S Pen悬浮于手机屏幕上方的任何位置，轻点笔杆的按钮，屏幕上就会自动弹出S Pen浮窗指令的5个常用的强大功能：智能备忘录、随剪随贴、截屏编写、S搜索和随笔窗口。S Pen浮窗指令可随时开启，省去了反复切换屏幕的麻烦，让您的任务处理更加轻松便捷。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g15/M02/0B/05/rBEhWVI6y3IIAAAAAABl3s9T4BUAADUJQHnXgUAAGX2845.jpg\" /></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">智能备忘录</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">下笔即来的便捷</span><br />GALAXY Note3的智能备忘录，能将您的笔迹直接连至7个常用的功能指令：通话、保存联系人信息、发信息、发邮件、搜索网页、地图搜索位置和添加任务。只需手写便条，即可为您执行相应指令，或是将您的手写信息转化为格式化的内容。当您记下某个目的地的名称，就能立即进入地图并找到相应位置；当您手写一个电话号码，就能直接转入通话或存储功能。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g15/M02/0B/05/rBEhWlI6y7IIAAAAAACbq0NfkSoAADUJQK-E48AAJvD721.jpg\" /></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">随剪随贴</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">随手创建资料库</span><br />GALAXY Note3的随剪随贴，让您轻松收集和组织各种不同种类的内容。无论是网页还是视频内容，它都能灵巧准确地为您剪出所需，并轻松创建专属于您的个性化资料库。任何您需要的信息，只需轻按S Pen按钮，选择随剪随贴功能，用笔圈出内容并进行编辑，然后保存到剪贴库即可。同时您也可以自行创建文件夹，依照主题分门别类。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g15/M02/0B/05/rBEhWVI6y94IAAAAAACXApdg8B8AADUJQN__LsAAJca478.jpg\" /></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">S搜索</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">随时搜索轻松找到</span><br />GALAXY Note3的S搜索，可随时根据您的指令进行最大范围的搜索，找出手机中的各种内容。只需点击S Pen 的按钮, 您可从任何界面直接到达S搜索功能，进行个人内容的导航和搜索。无论是相册主题还是聊天内容，甚至是您手写的符号，都能为您轻松找到。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g13/M05/0C/0C/rBEhUlI6zAEIAAAAAACb1YxBZBYAADT7QKn8AQAAJvt241.jpg\" /></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">随笔窗口</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">随心绘制开启窗口</span><br />想要快速启动常用应用程序，又不想来回切换窗口？GALAXY Note3令人惊叹的随笔窗口功能，助您轻松快捷地开启新的应用。您只需在屏幕的任意位置画一个任意尺寸大小的窗口，即可选择您想要开启新的应用。现在，您可以在写邮件时开启计算器功能，或是在浏览网页时拨打电话，在同一屏幕中尽享多种精彩。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g13/M06/0C/0C/rBEhU1I6zC0IAAAAAACRhNKJUU4AADT7gA7WqQAAJGc509.jpg\" /></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">多窗口多任务</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">运用自如游刃有余</span><br />GALAXY Note3的超强性能和超大屏幕，为您轻松实现多任务。您可以同时处理两项任务，或是开启两个不同的应用，还可以直接将文本、图片等内容拖拽到另一个窗口。无需关闭窗口或打开新页面，您就能在应用程序之间进行无缝切换。在浏览网页的同时，您可以发送短信给朋友，您甚至可以在两个窗口上运行同一个应用程序(如：网络浏览器、ChatON)。让您跟上快节奏的生活步伐，成为一名游刃有余的工作专家。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g15/M03/0B/05/rBEhWVI6zFkIAAAAAACBGeFiHzAAADUJgB7GdUAAIEx451.jpg\" /></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">我的资讯中心</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">海量资讯时尚阅读</span><br />GALAXY Note3的超大屏幕让您在浏览画面时，获得翻看时尚杂志般的新鲜视觉体验，满足您的需求。个性化的界面，让所有菜单一目了然。独特的界面设计，让您不仅可以轻松浏览新闻、社交媒体内容，还能畅享一键开启最常用功能的便捷。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g14/M02/11/05/rBEhVlI6zH4IAAAAAACXayBgbMoAADWgwAvCMQAAJeD005.jpg\" /></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">全新S Note</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">绘写精彩如您所愿</span><br />带上它，便拥有了一款性能完备的全新笔记本。S Note不仅具有笔记本式的简单界面，同时还提供丰富的制作模板。它能将快速潦草的笔记和素描编辑得非常美观，也能将您画出的形状和手写内容即时变成完美的图形和数字文本。全新升级的S Note如您所愿，打造精彩生活。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g14/M02/11/05/rBEhV1I6zKsIAAAAAAB1ZSx4iw0AADWgwF7wYcAAHV9919.jpg\" /></span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:32px;\">随笔输入</span></div><div class=\"formwork_titleleft\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:24px;\"><br /></span></div><div class=\"formwork_text\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">手写替代键盘输入</span><br />GALAXY Note3 具备进一步升级更加先进的手写识别技术，打破了之前只有<br />S Note功能才可进行手写识别的限制。现在，无论是日历、闹钟，还是发短信、拨打电话都可通过手写识别实现。</span></div></div><div class=\"formwork\"><div class=\"formwork_img\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g13/M06/0C/0C/rBEhUlI6zNkIAAAAAACB5vkZcP0AADT7gGd19sAAIH-086.jpg\" /></span></div></div></div>', '2015-03-08 21:27:49', '2015-03-08 21:27:49');
