tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table><p><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" width=\"750\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/jgsq-productsoa/g7/M00/0E/0F/rBEHZlClrQsIAAAAAAD-sMkQD9sAAC1FADldgMAAP7I398.jpg\" /><br /><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br /></span></td></tr></tbody></table></p><div dir=\"ltr\" id=\"imcontent\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family:\'Segoe UI\';color:#ff00ff;DIRECTION: ltr; WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"></span><table style=\"line-height: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px;\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><div><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 20.25pt; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 18px\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\">目前苹果公司iPhone4新批次系统版本是iOS7，新旧批次产品本身无质量差异。我司会随机发送新旧批次货物，<span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 1.5; MARGIN: 0px; FONT-FAMILY: \'Segoe UI\'; DIRECTION: ltr; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" id=\"2786146.0\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\" id=\"2786146.0\">iOS5</span></span></span>&nbsp;/iOS6</span></span></span>系统可升级至iOS7（为了系统升级安全，建议在电脑上进行），<span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 13.5pt\">具体操作系统事宜请咨询苹果公司官方售后支持电话：</span><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 13.5pt\">400-627-2273<span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\"><span style=\"MARGIN: 0px\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">，</span></span></span></span></span></span>请知晓。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><br /><br /><p></p>', '2015-03-08 21:33:18', '2015-03-08 21:33:18');
