INSERT INTO `tb_item_desc` VALUES ('1247118', '<div class=\"content_tpl\"><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-0\" name=\"detail-tag-id-0\" text=\"产品信息\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>产品信息</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Product Information</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t313/84/1447238808/566396/5b455e94/543ba0afNff6be3e4.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-2\" name=\"detail-tag-id-2\" text=\"产品特色\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>产品特色</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Selling Point</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t331/191/1498288233/184535/5375ac4c/543ba155Nd9667b04.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t274/11/1486214240/308917/14b729ed/543ba171Nc1e55f50.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">极致4K  超清体验     飞利浦超高清电视拥有3840&times;2160屏幕分辨率，提供震撼超清显示品质，从而展现无比细腻、分毫毕现的画面效果。																																			\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t298/256/1498630441/253613/680fe4cd/543ba1fcN98d7cce8.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">4K 引擎  智能优化  飞利浦超高清电视特有画质引擎---4K锐腾核芯，拥有超凡的运算能力，能够处理包括超高清信号在内的各类视频信号，对画面进行优化提升，呈现优异、清晰的超高清视频。																																			\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t313/354/1481809107/293136/1ccca4e9/543ba248N38eeb54e.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">优化画质   身临其境   4大画质处理技术，优化对比度提升细节表现力，智能降噪提升画质清晰度，自动增加色彩的鲜艳度，锐度提升图像层级感，让每一个画面，都宛如真境。																																			\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t316/90/1484943607/228616/cba59cc8/543ba264N050e810a.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">六核引擎  迅捷精彩    采用先进六核处理器----高效利用四核CPU运算，后台运行速度更快；双核GPU显著提升图形渲染能力，使得画面更加清晰、色彩还原更加逼真。通过六核处理，畅快淋漓的完美视效瞬间跃然眼前。 																																			\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t340/193/1492459894/228565/b6efd1b0/543ba459Na9047d5c.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">出色音箱  天籁之音   内置双音腔设计，采用&ldquo;隐身扬声器&rdquo;设计，能模拟出影院般逼真的环绕效果，营造非凡卓越的影音体验。																																			\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t310/131/1477014031/208037/9abb66cb/543ba4aaNfeff0d02.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">360度环绕     震撼心灵  飞利浦超宽环绕立体声，通过电子和声学原理处理信号，使您欣赏到层次丰富的立体声和身临其境般的虚拟环绕音效。																																			\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t646/59/365067485/399689/a1f663af/54605d2bN91dd5a40.png\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">Smart TV  Android 4.2平台   采用市场主流智能开放式平台  拥有更好的兼容性和稳定性  飞利浦应用商城   飞利浦专为电视定制的海量应用系统，给您更丰富精彩地应用体验。无论您是游戏控、炒股王、游戏狂还是社交达人，都能找到至爱。																																			\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t310/344/1469808046/271757/ecc7eaa9/543ba60aN90d9cd8f.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">芒果TV 在线视频   芒果TV内容平台拥有海量正版视频资讯，每日更新片库，为您提供最新最酷的影视资讯和新闻内容。\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t277/55/1479452304/215778/208905bb/543ba739Nfd54e69