INSERT INTO `tb_item_desc` VALUES ('1268156', '<div class=\"content_tpl\"><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t691/61/1183383748/502506/19f53a43/54ba1133Nfbef015b.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">   作为世界顶级的液晶面板制造公司，LG Display公司开发的IPS硬屏技术广泛应用在航天、汽车、医学、设计等高端科技领域，H18系列采用原装LG炫黑硬屏，液晶分子结构抗压性强、稳定性高，从而保证急速画面无拖影，同时还非常精准地还原最本真的色彩。</div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-2\" name=\"detail-tag-id-2\" text=\"产品功能\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>产品功能</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Product Function</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t523/142/1184018754/870284/88a366dd/54ba1160N7f14cc08.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    如今手机屏幕的分辨率已经达到甚至超过1080P，与手机形成鲜明对比的是，尺寸更大的电视机在分辨率上有的竟然还不如手机，电视机的1080P已经不能满足高清控的你，4K势必会带来更加强烈的视觉冲击，尤其是在40吋以上的电视，4K的普及是不可阻挡的趋势。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t655/190/1160870388/85458/e6d834f7/54ba1186N823f8842.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    如此之高的像素密度，你的肉眼根本看不出任何像素，因此，电视的画面呈现出难以置信的细节。最出色的清晰度，就是达到你肉眼所不能辨别的境界。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t706/176/500159749/236975/5c1649f6/54ba11dfN226b4fd0.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    由开山鼻祖的480P显现管电视发展到如今革命性的4K超高清电视，随着人们对电视的画面质量追求逐渐提高，4K电视，必定是未来客厅的标准。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t460/180/1174772794/569387/16a8f862/54ba1201N6ab1b51b.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    4K电视。让您的家和您更显尊贵品位。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t508/204/1187313794/319783/6853f71f/54ba12c3N72715f90.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    搭载了TCL全新2K转4K关联补偿技术，通过对1080P信号的实时分析，将信号划分为200万个二维区间，相邻区间进行纵向横向四个维度的色彩运算，同时把编码效率提高一倍，从而将1080P高清信号提升到4K超高清信号，图像真实度达到90%以上，比全高清状态下高出3倍以上。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t472/246/1212063429/1240960/b60cd319/54ba13cdNc348d7d2.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    华数为用户提供了快捷、稳定、流畅的视频观赏体验，精品影视任意畅享，人气综艺尽情点播，最新资讯及早知道。汇聚全网最新和最全的高清电影、电视剧、综艺、MV、新闻...你想看的，一点就播！</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t580/87/1209737929/652262/adec4e01/54ba13ecN0992340b.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    搭载了目前最高版本的安卓智能电视操作系统&mdash;&mdash;Android4.3,内置应用软件安装器，界面简练明晰，能够轻松安装U盘上的APK文件，轻松安装后即可使用。兼容绝大多数安卓APK软件，玩转电视就是那么简单。\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t685/159/1172466736/618910/a1b2e651/54ba1a32Ne2330707.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-18\" name=\"detail-tag-id-18\" text=\"产品展示\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>产品展示</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Products Exhibition</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t514/164/1174057271/652427/58bfc7e1/54ba1a74N1c1ec9e6.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    极简主义是未来值得我们去追求的生活方式。有人以为加法总是好的，缺不知减法才是精彩的极致。H18系列外观设计崇高简约，志在融入你家客厅，给你舒适生活。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t544/205/1175413040/142290/5618d5cf/54ba1aa5N1870365d.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    多给你一个爱上它的理由：霸气！如果你以为简约会削减它的气场，你就大错特错了。真正的霸气来自于它精良的做工、漂亮的外观和高造价的材质，自信，才会尽显霸气。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t745/212/534947350/209611/36132b25/54ba1ca7N97c1e764.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    不小心看见它侧面机身，你绝对会忍不住赞叹如此大的尺寸还能同时拥有这巧灵的机身，因为它可以为电视柜省出更多的空间，因为它可以与墙壁更为贴合，仟薄就是出众！</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t688/213/1227311090/337893/66e3a758/54ba1da2Ndb02e419.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    虽然很多人常常会忽视的后壳，但是TCL的设计师并没有因此敷衍背面设计。层叠式空间感设计、金属材质、散热孔布局、接口排列都这样井井有条，恰如其分。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t454/356/1191717227/210535/3cda4fb1/54ba1e95Nb82445de.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t580/40/1202367585/537884/5984f10d/54ba1ea4Ncfc154a2.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t520/143/1156453378/202866/b1b13cb0/54ba1eb6N7145cfc7.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-30\" name=\"detail-tag-id-30\" text=\"品牌介绍\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>品牌介绍</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Brand Introduction</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t685/131/1081675884/26436/8a01866/54ae4459N19fdc87d.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t661/60/1117289266/150325/deede591/54ae442bN14cde3f6.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t718/48/423744275/36393/98d638ce/54ae43fbNe0af7ab1.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t496/251/1076434824/100547/1d713b8e/54ae440fN6bd46368.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t643/64/1087681214/79209/56e05a91/54ae4434N189eef3f.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t469/29/1114123449/94213/1dd81e7/54ae4418N961f3128.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t541/80/1093226019/44957/604238fb/54ae4420Nea8f9592.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t754/91/413811318/92471/36f6b56f/54ae4405N00370fea.jpg\" /></div>\n</div></div>', '2015-03-08 21:27:45', '2015-03-08 21:27:45');
